    <title>centos7下安装emqx</title>
    <url>/2019/12/02/emqx%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="1-Install-the-required-dependencies"><a href="#1-Install-the-required-dependencies" class="headerlink" title="1. Install the required dependencies"></a>1. Install the required dependencies</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo yum install -y yum-utils device-mapper-persistent-data lvm2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="2-Set-up-a-stable-repository-taking-the-CentOS7-as-an-example"><a href="#2-Set-up-a-stable-repository-taking-the-CentOS7-as-an-example" class="headerlink" title="2. Set up a stable repository, taking the CentOS7 as an example."></a>2. Set up a stable repository, taking the CentOS7 as an example.</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo yum-config-manager --add-repo https://repos.emqx.io/emqx-ce/redhat/centos/7/emqx-ce.repo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="3-Install-the-latest-version-of-EMQ-X"><a href="#3-Install-the-latest-version-of-EMQ-X" class="headerlink" title="3. Install the latest version of EMQ X"></a>3. Install the latest version of EMQ X</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo yum install emqx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="4-Install-a-specific-version-of-EMQ-X"><a href="#4-Install-a-specific-version-of-EMQ-X" class="headerlink" title="4. Install a specific version of EMQ X"></a>4. Install a specific version of EMQ X</h2><h4 id="1-Query-available-version"><a href="#1-Query-available-version" class="headerlink" title="1. Query available version"></a>1. Query available version</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ yum list emqx --showduplicates | sort -remqx.x86_64 3.1.0-1.el7 emqx-stableemqx.x86_64 3.0.1-1.el7 emqx-stableemqx.x86_64 3.0.0-1.el7 emqx-stable</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="2-Install-a-specific-version-based-on-the-version-string-in-the-second-column-such-as-3-1-0"><a href="#2-Install-a-specific-version-based-on-the-version-string-in-the-second-column-such-as-3-1-0" class="headerlink" title="2. Install a specific version based on the version string in the second column, such as 3.1.0"></a>2. Install a specific version based on the version string in the second column, such as 3.1.0</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo yum install emqx-3.1.0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="5-Start-EMQ-X"><a href="#5-Start-EMQ-X" class="headerlink" title="5. Start EMQ X"></a>5. Start EMQ X</h2><h4 id="Directly-start-emqx-startemqx-3-1-0-is-started-successfully"><a href="#Directly-start-emqx-startemqx-3-1-0-is-started-successfully" class="headerlink" title="* Directly start$ emqx startemqx 3.1.0 is started successfully!"></a>* Directly start$ emqx startemqx 3.1.0 is started successfully!</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ emqx_ctl statusNode &apos;emqx@127.0.0.1&apos; is startedemqx v3.1.0 is running</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="systemctl-start"><a href="#systemctl-start" class="headerlink" title="* systemctl start"></a>* systemctl start</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ sudo systemctl start emqx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="service-start"><a href="#service-start" class="headerlink" title="* service start"></a>* service start</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># sudo su</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="6-访问应用"><a href="#6-访问应用" class="headerlink" title="6. 访问应用"></a>6. 访问应用</h2><pre><code>地址：http://IP:18083
用户名/密码：admin/public</code></pre>]]></content>
